title: Joakim Hykkerud
text:
Joakim André Hykkerud (born 10 February 1986) is a Norwegian <a href="handball">handball</a> player for <a href="Lemvig-Thybor%C3%B8n%20H%C3%A5ndbold">Lemvig-Thyborøn Håndbold</a> and the <a href="Norway%20men%27s%20national%20handball%20team">Norwegian national team</a>.
He competed at the <a href="2016%20European%20Men%27s%20Handball%20Championship">2016 European Men's Handball Championship</a>.
